title: How to Install a Thule Crossroad Railing Foot Pack 450
description: This easy-to-install accessory converts your existing factory rack with raised side rails into full-featured Thule rack system. See all the simple steps here!

asset.title: Roof Racks - Thule Crossroad Railing Foot Pack 450
asset.description:
Watch this video and learn step by step how to install the Thule Crossroad Railing Foot Pack 450 on the roof of your car.

Thule Crossroad Railing Foot Pack 450
Converts existing factory rack with raised side rails into full-featured Thule rack system.

- Built-in tool for easy installation and removal
- Rubber coated steel strap secures foot to siderail

Learn more at http://www.thule.com
